jobs.name: Daily trends scan (TikTok/YouTube/X)
jobs.description: Scan trends and extract product content angles for TikTok, YouTube, X.

payload.message: Scan today’s trends on TikTok, YouTube, and X relevant to our product niche. Output: 10 trend bullets, 10 hooks, 5 product angles, and 3 content series ideas. Keep it concise and actionable.

jobs.name: Daily short-form scripts
jobs.description: Draft short-form scripts for TikTok/YouTube/X from trend inputs.

payload.message: Create 3 short-form scripts (<=45s) and 5 tweet/X post drafts based on yesterday’s trend scan. Include: hook, body beats, CTA. Format as a ready-to-post checklist.

jobs.name: Daily offer packaging
jobs.description: Refine product offer, CTA, and landing copy snippets.

payload.message: Refine product offer for today’s content. Output: 1 primary CTA, 2 alternate CTAs, 3 headline variants, 3 subhead variants, and 5 bullets focusing on value + proof.

jobs.name: Weekly revenue pipeline review
jobs.description: Weekly revenue checklist and next actions.

payload.message: Weekly revenue review. Summarize: content output, engagement, funnel status, sales blockers, and top 5 actions for next week. Use concise bullets.

jobs.name: Daily content calendar (TikTok/YouTube/X)
jobs.description: Plan daily posting slots, topics, and CTAs for TikTok, YouTube, and X.

payload.message: Build today’s content calendar for TikTok, YouTube, and X. Output: 3 posting slots with topic, hook, CTA, and target audience. Keep it concise.

jobs.name: Daily YouTube long-form outline
jobs.description: Create a long-form YouTube outline based on top trend/offer.

payload.message: Draft a 6–10 minute YouTube video outline based on the top trend/offer. Include: title options, hook, 5–7 beats, CTA, and thumbnail text ideas.

jobs.name: Daily engagement playbook
jobs.description: Generate engagement replies and community prompts for TikTok/YouTube/X.

payload.message: Create an engagement playbook for today: 10 reply templates, 5 community prompts, and 5 DMs ideas tailored to TikTok, YouTube, and X.

jobs.name: Weekly batch production plan
jobs.description: Plan weekly batch filming/writing for TikTok/YouTube/X.

payload.message: Weekly batch production plan: list 10 short-form video ideas, 3 long-form ideas, filming order, and a 2-hour production schedule.

jobs.name: Daily KPI snapshot
jobs.description: Create a daily KPI checklist to track views, CTR, and conversions.

payload.message: Daily KPI snapshot template for TikTok/YouTube/X: metrics to log, target ranges, and a 5-bullet daily optimization plan.
